But aggro is generated regardless of resist or not. Our taunt button is equivlent to yelling at the TV..... they cant hear you its like it never happend. Thats the whole point of this part of the discussion.. warriors total lack of ability to keep aggro without weapons that are out of reach of alot of warriors in the 51-59 range. Warriors have the highest cap on taunt skill because it is the only innate ability we have to aquire aggro, and it doesnt work as well as it should. As I have stated before and I'll say it again.. I don't want GAURANTEED AGGRO with one push of a button.. but to at least have a chance for it to work would be nice. At my level and in my current gear I can tank mobs in say Umbral Plains just fine, but my inablity to taunt them cripples me in this zone, I basically become a third rate damage dealer with some bandages.<br>
 <p><div align="center"><embed width="468" height="148" src="http://www.ameritech.net/users/amplified/SWSig.swf"></div><BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uchavr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>chavr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/7/02 9:37:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=907.topic&index=377>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_die.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: I'm confused...</span><hr size=1> So this isn't a thread about warriors being behind other classes.  It's a thread about taunt being broken at 55+?<br>
<br>
If the problem lies with a taunt not working at a certain level or higher then why not rally the support of both sk's and paladins to get taunt fixed for us all.  <br>
<br>
Like I stated previously, I have no problem fixing a broken part of a class.  My problem is with the concept of the original post implying/stating that paladins are greater then warriors and warriors need an upgrade to make them better then paladins.<br>
